{"tid":1483951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地客子女擬返內地升學 撻租豪廷峰","createTime":"2019-08-18T13:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:25:48.000Z","uid":53026,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7afa02b1c253cb6f09eef3d0e5c933e86c4971d7","tid":1483951,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"內地客子女擬返內地升學 撻租豪廷峰<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】社會氣氛持續嚴峻，有個別內地客選擇撻租本港物業。中原區域營業董事林龍南表示，北角豪廷峰2座高層E室，屬實用面積790方呎三房戶，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原獲內地客以月租4萬元承租，實用呎租近51元，惟社會運動持續，該內地客擬讓子女返內地讀書，最後撻租離場。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林指出，上述豪廷峰單位已重新於市場放租，現每月叫租4.3萬元、即每呎叫租54.4元，租金加幅7.5%；以業主1999年購入價682.9萬元計，料可享7.6厘租金回報。<br />\n<br />\n部分市區屋苑仍錄得高價租務成交，中原首席分區經理楊文傑表示，鰂魚涌近期入伙的君豪峰，高層M室以1.6萬元租出，屬實用面積214方呎開放式戶，實用呎租74.8元，創屋苑呎租新高，較舊紀錄70元高出約7%。業主去年以562萬元買入，享租金回報3.4厘。<br />\n君豪峰開放式戶呎租75元破頂<br />\n<br />\n另鑽石山星河明居B座高層2室，實用面積517方呎，新近以月租2.37萬元租出，實用呎租近46元，創屋苑新高，較舊紀錄44元高出4.5%。業主2007年以325萬元購入單位，租金回報高見8.8厘。香港置業首席聯席董事周世康表示，灣仔囍匯中低層G室，屬1房複式間隔，實用面積584方呎，業主以約3.5萬元放租約半個月後獲區內客洽詢，並「零議價」租出，實用呎租約60元，新租客為外籍人士。業主去年以1608萬元購入單位，租金回報2.6厘。"},{"pid":"a30a75f308c10ae31c8459962ace4d3e0becfddc","tid":1483951,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"小鳯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdd95e9aa389dd4d8805eb5856ddc1d5564104e","tid":1483951,"uid":3239,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"撻租離場仲叫高左<br />\n即係物業回報增加<br />\n要多謝社會運動帶動香港經濟逆難而上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5ac8e9616c83754b2e98a3ea29a1fd70dc763e","tid":1483951,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5cdd95e9aa389dd4d8805eb5856ddc1d5564104e","tid":1483951,"uid":3239,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"撻租離場仲叫高左<br />\n即係物業回報增加<br />\n要多謝社會運動帶動香港經濟逆難而上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"好可能又係租返俾大陸人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一雞死，.........<br />\n未開學而已。"},{"pid":"3f1dbdb2b723bbb075ccc8b637305ea2bdcedbe0","tid":1483951,"uid":282347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:51:44.000Z","msg":"香港咁多暴徒，蚛蟈人返去佢地安全嘅蚛蟈喇，唔好再係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cb4defd523a081f07ab16b6d7e34a641064344","tid":1483951,"uid":67338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"非常好<br />\n來擁抱大灣區榮耀吧"},{"pid":"867b92b343735fa5d2286868cfe141b88bf4cdcd","tid":1483951,"uid":35457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"北角，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abb6cc2c71e073fdc82f2b4b34d9e97ce9c84fc","tid":1483951,"uid":103363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:12:14.000Z","msg":"請撻唔好再留係香港，番去大灣區啦"},{"pid":"f81ebba671b990aff14ad813ebb2f8654344d900","tid":1483951,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"撻租你仲開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52af979829c6f149de25c16b7735d5e0058b6d5f","tid":1483951,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"北角d垃圾地方撚值咁貴<br />\n又嘈又污糟又多大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61106d68dfaf045ef65991a96371199dae0275e4","tid":1483951,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52af9798